libs.content:
find_library(lua_library
  names lua lua52 lua5.2 lua51 lua5.1 lua
  hints
  $env{lua_dir}
  ${lua_hints}
  path_suffixes lib64 lib
  paths
  ~/library/frameworks
  /library/frameworks
  /usr/local
  /usr
  /sw
  /opt/local
  /opt/csw
  /opt
)

find_program(lynx_executable
  names
    lynx
    elinks
    links
    true
  paths
    ${cygwin_install_path}/bin
    /bin
    /usr/bin
    /usr/local/bin
    /sbin
)

find_library(
    _glib2_link_dir
  names
    ${_glib2_link_dir}
    glib-2.0
    glib
  paths
    ${glib2_library_dirs}
    /opt/gnome/lib
    /opt/local/lib
    /sw/lib
    /usr/lib
    /usr/local/lib
  hints
    "${glib2_hints}/lib"
  )

find_library( nl_library
      names
        nl-3 nl
      path_suffixes
        lib64 lib
      paths
        $(searchpaths)
    )

find_library( nlgenl_library
      names
        nl-genl-3 nl-genl
      path_suffixes
        lib64 lib
      paths
        $(searchpaths)
    )

find_library( nlroute_library
      names
        nl-route-3 nl-route
      path_suffixes
        lib64 lib
      paths
        $(searchpaths)
    )

find_library( nl_library
      names
        nl
      path_suffixes
        lib64 lib
      paths
        $(searchpaths)
    )
find_library( gmodule2_libraries names gmodule-2.0 gmodule hints "${gmodule2_hints}/lib" )

find_program(html_viewer_executable
  names
    xdg-open
    mozilla
    htmlview
    open
    $env{html_viewer}
  paths
    ${cygwin_install_path}/bin
    /bin
    /usr/bin
    /usr/local/bin
    /sbin
)
